&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: medium;"&gt;* Saiba mais &lt;a href="http://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Instagram" target="_blank"&gt;sobre Instagram no Wikipédia&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Apr 2012 09:47:51 +0000</pubDate><link>http://softwarelivre.org/furusho/blog/um-milhao-de-download-do-instagram-android-em-um-unico-dia.-e-5-milhoes-em-apenas-6-dias.</link><guid>http://softwarelivre.org/furusho/blog/um-milhao-de-download-do-instagram-android-em-um-unico-dia.-e-5-milhoes-em-apenas-6-dias.</guid></item></channel></rss>